{"tid":25394,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《你的名字》大陸擬拍真人版 景甜驚傳演三葉","createTime":"2016-12-06T05:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T08:26:42.000Z","uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7d5cc1c5e5084bc2802f536feedce05eb7c4bc1","tid":25394,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:54:44.000Z","msg":"新海誠作品《你的名字。》喺大陸上映幾日已經收3億人民幣，票房走勢持續凌厲，唔少強國觀眾都暫時拋開反日情緒，仲傳出開拍大陸真人版消息。<br />\n<br />\n《你的名字。》引起大陸網民熱烈討論，噚日就傳出已有製作公司趁住新海誠上月去北京時傾掂數，仲買斷埋翻拍版權，內容講到似層層，仲話會起用EXO舊將鹿晗夥拍有後台撐腰打入荷李活嘅景甜做主角。出到買斷埋翻拍版權呢招咁絕？<br />\n雖然景甜、鹿晗演主角三葉同瀧嘅傳聞似流料多啲，不過強國要開拍真人版《你的名字。》的確係有跡可尋，事關新海誠舊作《秒速5厘米》早已被大陸片商買下版權開拍電影，更何況呢套作品近期大熱。<br />\n不過，唔少網民都擔心到時大陸版又會毀咗呢套大好作品，唔知原作中嘅靚景，到時會變成乜嘢景點取景？係咪會去行長城、遊故宮？<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161206/large/1480995423_ede2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161206%2Flarge%2F1480995423_ede2.jpg&h=0399d160&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51be4c70d79c25670d09e44e9008d6c7f4248cd3","tid":25394,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82cd4c6a52d5375593def87cbc621af2b27d385a","tid":25394,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:20:15.000Z","msg":"嘩 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01046cf00e2fe0e855fcd26c967a36062520395","tid":25394,"uid":1152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:59:23.000Z","msg":"又景甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe54a1bb4b251840359876c4c6e79c29ec7eeee","tid":25394,"uid":4260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:20:33.000Z","msg":"景甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced99150074919a3f399c5ca0dc1fae23c1c48a6","tid":25394,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:26:42.000Z","msg":"原來景甜係人名黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}